The paper deals with the performance evaluation of a MISO wireless communication system incorporating Turbo encoding and Q-STBC scheme. This involves the use of signal detection schemes and digital modulations. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Communications (cs.COM) sub-categories.
